# Edge case: alignment inside a subrange. `Inner` has only an align field, so
# its padding size is determined purely by the offset zero-point policy at the
# subrange boundary: absolute (inherit parent offset) vs subrange-local (reset
# to 0). Decided: absolute (inherit). See docs/decisions/0038.
format EdgeCase:
    len :u16
    inner :Inner(input = input.subrange(len))

format Inner:
    align :[..]u8(input.align = 32)
